You bought these?

565
00:32:00,946 --> 00:32:03,786
Miss An, you got these for us?

566
00:32:04,786 --> 00:32:06,266
You really think so?

567
00:32:06,512 --> 00:32:07,386
- No.
- Not really.

568
00:32:08,306 --> 00:32:08,786
Really?

569
00:32:08,786 --> 00:32:09,546
Who got these?

570
00:32:15,826 --> 00:32:16,346
Hello?

571
00:32:16,826 --> 00:32:18,786
Miss An, you got the delivery?

572
00:32:18,786 --> 00:32:20,506
These are the gifts for proposals

573
00:32:20,506 --> 00:32:21,586
from innovative startups.

574
00:32:21,826 --> 00:32:23,666
It's our new regulation.

575
00:32:24,346 --> 00:32:25,426
Wish you success.

576
00:32:26,346 --> 00:32:28,826
Please thank Miss Lan
and the shareholders for us.

577
00:32:28,826 --> 00:32:29,826
We will do our best.

578
00:32:30,786 --> 00:32:31,386
Bye.

579
00:32:33,346 --> 00:32:35,626
These are from Lansheng Investment.

580
00:32:37,346 --> 00:32:38,346
Open them.

581
00:32:38,346 --> 00:32:39,066
Here we go.

582
00:32:39,066 --> 00:32:40,506
Graphics tablets. My goodness.

583
00:32:40,866 --> 00:32:42,706
A whole box of tea leaves.

584
00:32:43,266 --> 00:32:43,826
I'll take it.

585
00:32:44,346 --> 00:32:46,106
The biggest one is gone.

586
00:32:46,106 --> 00:32:47,946
Let me help. It's so heavy.

587
00:32:47,946 --> 00:32:48,706
Sure.

588
00:32:49,706 --> 00:32:50,426
Peng.

589
00:32:52,866 --> 00:32:54,666
It paints better scenes with that.

590
00:32:55,346 --> 00:32:56,106
Try it.

591
00:33:09,904 --> 00:33:11,856
(Everything will go well.)

592
00:33:27,826 --> 00:33:28,426
Hello?

593
00:33:29,026 --> 00:33:29,946
Got the delivery?

594
00:33:30,866 --> 00:33:32,506
I was about to call you.

595
00:33:32,866 --> 00:33:35,106
I made myself clear last time.

596
00:33:35,106 --> 00:33:36,706
Why are you still pestering me?

597
00:33:37,186 --> 00:33:38,826
I just want to help your company.

598
00:33:39,106 --> 00:33:42,626
Mr. Pei, our proposal
will be approved anyway.

599
00:33:42,866 --> 00:33:45,186
Please stop sending us things

600
00:33:45,186 --> 00:33:46,386
in the name of Miss Lan.

601
00:33:55,266 --> 00:33:56,026
Bai Mengyao.

602
00:34:01,306 --> 00:34:02,106
What's wrong?

603
00:34:02,626 --> 00:34:03,266
It's yours now.

604
00:34:05,104 --> 00:34:06,186
A fountain pen?

605
00:34:07,472 --> 00:34:08,666
Doesn't it look nice?

606
00:34:11,346 --> 00:34:12,586
Pei Jun gave it to you?

607
00:34:16,346 --> 00:34:18,266
Return it if you don't like it.

608
00:34:19,106 --> 00:34:20,186
Why would I?

609
00:34:20,586 --> 00:34:22,506
He can give me gifts all he wants.

610
00:34:22,506 --> 00:34:24,146
I can decide what to do with them.

611
00:34:24,976 --> 00:34:27,346
Think twice. I'll leave it here.

612
00:34:40,912 --> 00:34:42,106
Why are you here?

613
00:34:44,706 --> 00:34:46,546
I thought we'd meet at the studio.

614
00:34:49,106 --> 00:34:50,346
I came to tell you that

615
00:34:50,866 --> 00:34:52,866
I'm sick today and won't go to work.

616
00:34:55,066 --> 00:34:56,106
What's wrong?

617
00:35:00,346 --> 00:35:01,546
Do you want a ride?

618
00:35:01,546 --> 00:35:02,906
Let's get some medicine.

619
00:35:02,906 --> 00:35:04,866
We'll carry on with work
once you're better.

620
00:35:05,866 --> 00:35:06,346
No.

621
00:35:07,906 --> 00:35:10,706
Why are you so willful?

622
00:35:13,506 --> 00:35:15,664
Deal with that fountain pen
first, Miss An.

623
00:35:16,906 --> 00:35:18,586
I'm sick. I'm leaving.

624
00:35:22,426 --> 00:35:24,906
You could have just called me.

625
00:35:29,706 --> 00:35:31,346
Just give me a break.

626
00:35:43,696 --> 00:35:45,264
(Cefixime Capsules)

627
00:36:20,026 --> 00:36:21,106
Little brat.

628
00:36:47,696 --> 00:36:48,666
Why are you staring?

629
00:36:50,346 --> 00:36:53,506
Mr. Heisha certainly looks cool
when he's at work.

630
00:36:57,626 --> 00:36:58,906
What's wrong? Blushing?

631
00:37:01,586 --> 00:37:03,186
Are you going to stay there?

632
00:37:10,786 --> 00:37:13,106
Are you better today?

633
00:37:15,266 --> 00:37:15,866
Kind of.

634
00:37:17,866 --> 00:37:20,306
These are letters from your audience?

635
00:37:21,106 --> 00:37:23,026
Yeah. And they're handwritten.

636
00:37:23,386 --> 00:37:24,786
Handwritten?

637
00:37:25,186 --> 00:37:27,426
That's rare nowadays.

638
00:37:27,984 --> 00:37:29,266
What did they write?

639
00:37:29,626 --> 00:37:31,666
Mostly their feedback on Heisha Time

640
00:37:31,666 --> 00:37:33,306
and the dubbing I worked on.

641
00:37:33,626 --> 00:37:36,146
Some of them are their love stories.

642
00:37:36,706 --> 00:37:38,866
I would pick from those stories

643
00:37:39,106 --> 00:37:40,826
and share them in the show.

644
00:37:41,146 --> 00:37:43,146
This is one way for us to communicate.

645
00:37:44,866 --> 00:37:46,106
These are the read ones?

646
00:37:46,666 --> 00:37:47,626
These are unread?

647
00:37:48,266 --> 00:37:48,866
That's right.

648
00:37:49,146 --> 00:37:50,306
What about that?

649
00:37:52,346 --> 00:37:54,106
It's also unread. Want to read it?

650
00:37:54,706 --> 00:37:55,626
I can read it?

651
00:38:01,936 --> 00:38:05,146
(Sir Heisha, your voice is awful.)

652
00:38:05,146 --> 00:38:05,786
What's wrong?

653
00:38:07,026 --> 00:38:11,506
It turns out your audience
is people of all ages.

654
00:38:12,626 --> 00:38:15,346
Sir Heisha, your voice is awful.

655
00:38:15,346 --> 00:38:16,506
So awful.

656
00:38:16,506 --> 00:38:17,266
Are we gonna dub?

657
00:38:17,906 --> 00:38:18,426
Of course.

658
00:38:18,866 --> 00:38:19,386
Let's go.

659
00:38:30,586 --> 00:38:31,786
(Please don't be sad.)

660
00:38:32,466 --> 00:38:34,466
(You don't have to hide your old wounds)

661
00:38:35,226 --> 00:38:36,496
(and swallow your sorrow alone.)

662
00:38:37,346 --> 00:38:38,386
(I will stand by you)

663
00:38:38,706 --> 00:38:40,746
(and create new memories with you.)

664
00:38:41,392 --> 00:38:44,026
(I know you're working hard
to achieve your dream.)

665
00:38:44,746 --> 00:38:47,506
(I support you no matter what.)

666
00:38:48,826 --> 00:38:50,946
(For me, you're always the best.)

667
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:28,048
♪The movie told an undulating
and complicated story♪

668
