♪And there is only one possibility
between us♪

669
00:39:37,530 --> 00:39:42,320
♪We entangle ourselves in love♪

670
00:39:43,289 --> 00:39:45,904
♪What are you thinking about♪

671
00:39:45,904 --> 00:39:49,648
♪Where should I stand♪

672
00:39:49,648 --> 00:39:51,664
♪From the strange to the familiar♪

673
00:39:51,664 --> 00:39:54,288
♪From the familiar to the strange,
it's an inevitable part of love♪

674
